with ctrl +q (quick analysis)
you will be able to quickly create a chart

to create a chart within the 'insert' tab
is sufficient to select a cell in the data (not necessary to select all the data)

in the chart you can filter some Data

you can also switch x axis with y axis

to edit the colours go on the tab 'Format'

to save the chart as a template, click right
and select 'Save chart template'

save in the default folder of excel otherwise
excel will not see your template
 
